    <keyword>blkdiag</keyword>
    <short_description>Matrice diagonale par blocs</short_description>
    <syntax>
        <syntax_item>R = blkdiag(M1, ... , MN)</syntax_item>
    </syntax>
    <param_input>
        <param_input_item>
            <param_name>M1, ..., MN</param_name>
            <param_description>une matrice numérique 2D</param_description>
        </param_input_item>
    </param_input>
    <param_output>
        <param_output_item>
            <param_name>R</param_name>
            <param_description>une matrice.</param_description>
        </param_output_item>
    </param_output>
    <description>
        <p>
            <b
      >R = blkdiag(M1, ... , MN)</b> construit la matrice diagonale par blocs obtenue en alignant les matrices d'entrée <b
      >M1, ... , MN</b> le long de la diagonale de <b>R</b>.</p>
        </description>
